name: May (Pokemon Ruby/Sapphire)
description:
LoRa used to generate images of the character May from Pokémon in her Ruby/Sapphire outfit.

The main trigger tag used is may-rs. Additional tags used to describe the outfit are bandana, collared shirt, two-tone gloves, fanny pack, bike shorts. Not including these tags or putting them in the negative prompts should also remove the associated clothing from the generated image.

Issues:

  • The pokéball pattern on the bandana may end up a bit funky at times or invert the red/white colors.

  • More than two bandana ends may show up.

  • Gloves may end up either completely white or completely black. Putting white gloves and/or black gloves in the negatives may solve this problem.

  • A yellow backpack may occasionally be generated instead of a fanny pack. Putting yellow backpack in the negatives mostly solves this problem.

  • The white skirt-thing is occasionally forgotten.

  • Shoes aren't entirely accurate, since they weren't included in the prompt training.

Some details:

  • Base model: NAI

  • Trained on 98 handpicked images of variable sizes

    • 67 normal outfit, 31 alternate outfits

    • Watermarks + text manually edited out

    • Captions generated using SD WebUI dataset tag editor
